28
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:05,200
Very good.

29
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:06,200
You've done well.

30
00:02:06,719 --> 00:02:07,959
Once the tournament ends,

31
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:08,840
that Immortal Artifact

32
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,319
