69
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:53,319
Whether your Imperial Capital wants

70
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,599
to contend for supremacy,

71
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,120
or ignite the flames of war,

72
