73
00:03:59,599 --> 00:04:00,879
I only want that Immortal Artifact.

74
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,960
It's the instrument of my Divine Blessing.

75
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,759
With it,

76
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:08,840
