82
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:23,800
Sky City is one of the Eight Major Cities.

83
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,480
Once the dust settles,

84
00:04:25,839 --> 00:04:27,199
I'll deliver the Immortal Artifact

85
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,360
