88
00:04:48,399 --> 00:04:49,519
This world only needs

89
00:04:49,519 --> 00:04:51,480
one Imperial Capital, and that's enough.

90
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:55,920
I'm really looking forward to that day.

91
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,720
Gu Changkong and Gu Changye scheme deeply.

92
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:29,040
Neither will yield the Immortal Artifact.

93
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:30,639
From here on,

94
00:05:31,199 --> 00:05:33,120
I'll likely be their primary target.

95
00:05:33,959 --> 00:05:34,879
To be safe,

96
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,519
I'm leaving the group chat first.

97
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:48,839
Sangou.

98
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,839
Outside Black Street,

99
00:05:51,959 --> 00:05:53,839
