113
00:06:21,079 --> 00:06:21,879
I'm sure all of you

114
00:06:21,879 --> 00:06:24,120
have been looking forward to this match.

115
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:24,920
That's right.

116
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,959
We can see on the stage,

117
00:06:25,959 --> 00:06:27,519
Wu Kai from Jing City

118
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:29,120
and Wu Qianqiu from Tianshui City

119
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,240
