120
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,879
Their builds differ drastically,

121
00:06:31,879 --> 00:06:33,120
but as for the outcome,

122
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,639
let's wait and see.

123
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:37,240
Wu Kai of Jing City, here to face you.

124
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:40,199
Tianshui's

125
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,439
Wu Qianqiu.

126
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,360
No need to doubt it.

127
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,600
In the face of absolute power,

128
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,399
