134
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:10,240
I'm sure you've all seen

135
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,600
the results on the big screen.

136
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,240
Yes.

137
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,920
The small cities advancing to the top eight

138
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,879
are as follows:

139
00:07:15,079 --> 00:07:15,920
Heavenly Fire City,

140
00:07:15,959 --> 00:07:16,879
Tianshui City,

141
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:17,879
Starlight City,

142
00:07:17,879 --> 00:07:18,720
Jingtian City,

143
00:07:18,879 --> 00:07:19,800
Huicao City,

144
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:20,800
Yunlan City,

145
00:07:20,959 --> 00:07:21,959
Yangui City,

146
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:23,120
Shuangyue City.

147
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:25,040
Let's congratulate these eight cities

148
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:27,040
for standing out among the hundred,

149
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:29,199
qualifying to challenge the major cities.

150
00:07:31,759 --> 00:07:32,519
Everyone,

151
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:35,120
