153
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,199
Good luck!

154
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:43,959
The quarterfinal draws are out.

155
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:46,639
The next city challenging us

156
00:07:49,879 --> 00:07:50,600
is Heavenly Fire City.

157
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,759
I watched their matches in advance.

158
00:07:53,079 --> 00:07:53,879
Their strength is average,

159
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:57,120
far weaker than Starlight and Tianshui.

160
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,720
Against us,

161
00:07:58,959 --> 00:07:59,920
their odds of winning

162
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:00,879
are zero.

163
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,600
Alright.

164
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:12,759
Honestly, I still can't figure out

165
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:16,000
what the quarterfinal format designer

166
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:18,199
was actually thinking.

167
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:19,879
No individual matches,

168
00:08:19,879 --> 00:08:21,240
no team matches,

169
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:24,079
just five people taking turns to fight.

170
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:25,160
The winner

171
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:27,000
stays on the stage.

172
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,519
The loser

173
00:08:27,519 --> 00:08:28,639
gets swapped out for the next.

174
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:32,320
It ignores overall team strength.

175
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,919
As long as one person is strong enough,

176
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,639
he can wipe out the whole opposing team.

177
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:37,799
But thankfully,

178
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,919
this time on our team

179
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:40,960
