180
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,840
So,

181
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,480
I'm actually very satisfied

182
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:45,840
with the Imperial Capital's format.

183
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,759
How about it, Su Yang?

184
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,639
Got the confidence to take on five?

185
00:08:50,519 --> 00:08:51,320
Does it really have anything

186
00:08:52,039 --> 00:08:53,639
to do with my confidence?

187
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,440
Pointless.

188
00:08:56,159 --> 00:08:58,519
It's pointless to even talk to you.

189
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,679
Wasting your precious time.

190
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:05,279
I had expert analysts run the numbers.

191
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,279
Given Heavenly Fire City's strength,

192
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:09,399
we don't need to send Su Yang in.

193
00:09:09,879 --> 00:09:10,440
So that means

194
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,960
we can give you a chance to shine,

195
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,120
I mean,

196
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:15,440
a chance

197
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:20,000
to bring glory to Shanhai City.

198
00:09:27,519 --> 00:09:28,720
So tomorrow,

199
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,120
Yu Shuai goes first.

200
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:34,519
Your Divine Blessing is pretty flashy,

201
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:37,120
so it'll grab the audience's attention.

202
00:09:37,559 --> 00:09:38,159
Zhong Yun,

203
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,440
you're second.

204
00:09:39,919 --> 00:09:40,759
If

205
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:41,960
the first opponent

206
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:44,799
gets badly wounded by Yu Shuai,

207
00:09:44,919 --> 00:09:47,080
then you just go up and throw a couple punches,

208
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,720
and walk off in style.

209
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:50,399
If they aren't badly wounded,

210
00:09:50,399 --> 00:09:52,000
just surrender right away.

211
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,600
Xu Siguo goes third.

212
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:56,559
Liu Xiaorou fourth.

213
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,360
Su Yang as the closer, any objections?

214
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,840
Name of Heavenly Fire City's captain?

215
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:02,799
He's called

216
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,679
Fatty Zhao with a cleaver.

217
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:11,679
So,

218
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:14,480
you laid out all these messy tactics,

219
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:16,000
what does any of it have to do with this?

220
00:10:16,559 --> 00:10:19,159
Are you just trying to prove your worth

221
00:10:19,279 --> 00:10:20,200
