222
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:21,360
No, no.

223
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:24,440
I know Fatty Zhao is a Black Street guy,

224
00:10:24,759 --> 00:10:25,919
but some things,

225
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,759
you just can't say out loud.

226
00:10:27,919 --> 00:10:28,480
Right?

227
00:10:29,519 --> 00:10:30,080
Alright.

228
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:31,240
So tomorrow,

229
00:10:31,879 --> 00:10:34,600
we'll officially make Shanhai City's name

230
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,559
echo throughout the Hundred Cities.

231
00:10:37,799 --> 00:10:38,600
Are we confident?

232
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:41,639
Yes! Yes!

233
00:10:43,679 --> 00:10:44,320
Meeting adjourned.

234
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,720
I'm really glad

235
00:11:18,159 --> 00:11:20,360
I pulled you on board for this tournament.

236
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:22,840
Black Street folks are way more reliable.

237
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:25,399
Look at the Eight Major Cities' leaders,

238
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:27,600
