243
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:36,000
Come on, listen to yourself.

244
00:11:36,279 --> 00:11:37,559
I'm broke, aren't I?

245
00:11:37,679 --> 00:11:38,600
If I had money,

246
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,919
I wouldn't be out here hustling either.

247
00:11:41,159 --> 00:11:41,840
Get in.

248
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:46,960
Why are you riding in my carriage?

249
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:49,759
Because

250
00:11:50,799 --> 00:11:53,360
we only rented our bus for one day.

251
00:11:53,799 --> 00:11:54,240
Get in.

252
00:12:05,679 --> 00:12:06,120
Hyah!

253
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:27,120
Shanhai City, Yu Shuai, No. 3

254
00:12:27,279 --> 00:12:29,519
Sakura City, Su Qing, No. 6

255
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:31,759
Yunhua City, Xiao Zeyi, No. 5

256
00:12:32,039 --> 00:12:34,720
Heavenly Fire City, Zhao Qiansun, No. 3

257
00:12:34,879 --> 00:12:36,039
Based on the draw results,

258
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:37,320
today's first round match

259
00:12:37,399 --> 00:12:39,919
is Shanhai City versus Heavenly Fire City.

260
00:12:40,039 --> 00:12:40,679
That's right.

261
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:42,320
Will Heavenly Fire City manage to defeat

262
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:44,120
Shanhai City, one of Eight Major Cities,

263
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,120
and pull off an upset?

264
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:47,039
Who will come out on top?

265
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,720
Let's wait and see.

266
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:49,840
First match:

267
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:53,600
Shanhai City's Yu Shuai vs. Heavenly Fire City's Zhao Qiansun.

268
00:12:57,679 --> 00:12:59,919
A true Eight Major Cities contender.

269
00:12:59,919 --> 00:13:00,840
Such incredible composure!

270
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:01,639
I have to say,

271
00:13:01,639 --> 00:13:03,360
when I called the Hundred Cities knockouts,

272
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,879
some folks stepping into the arena

273
00:13:04,879 --> 00:13:06,320
were already shaking like leaves.

274
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,399
Now let's take a look at

275
00:13:07,399 --> 00:13:09,000
Heavenly Fire City's contestant,

276
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,159
Zhao Qiansun.

277
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:12,519
What a memorable name!

278
00:13:12,679 --> 00:13:14,600
He constantly carried his four teammates,

279
00:13:14,639 --> 00:13:15,960
a truly god-like presence.

280
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:18,320
Are we talking a bit too much?

281
00:13:19,039 --> 00:13:20,440
Then enough chatter,

282
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:22,039
the match officially begins!

283
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:24,720
This kid is way too cowardly.

284
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,360
He's about to wet himself.

285
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:29,440
Looking this lame against other teams,

286
00:13:29,759 --> 00:13:31,480
